parameters.name: R
parameters.description: Distance of Pioneer 11 from Jupiter, in Jupiter RADII (1 Jupiter radii is 71372 KM).

parameters.name: LAT
parameters.description: Latitude of Pioneer 11 in System III (1957.0), measured from the equator, positive northward.

parameters.name: LON1
parameters.description: Longitude of Pioneer 11 in System I, west longitude.

parameters.name: LON3
parameters.description: Longitude of Pioneer 11 in System III (1957.0), west longitude.

parameters.name: BX
parameters.description: X-component of the magnetic field in Inertial Heliocentric coordinates.

parameters.name: BY
parameters.description: Y-component of the magnetic field in Inertial Heliocentric coordinates.

parameters.name: BZ
parameters.description: Z-component of the magnetic field in Inertial Heliocentric coordinates.

parameters.name: BR
parameters.description: Radial component of the magnetic field in System III (1957.0), positive away from Jupiter.

parameters.name: BTHETA
parameters.description: Polar component of the magnetic field in System III (1957.0), positive northward.

parameters.name: BPHI
parameters.description: Azimuthal component of the magnetic field in System III (1957.0), positive eastward.

parameters.name: N
parameters.description: Number of data points used in averaging.
